<row>
<entry valign="top" align="left" namest="c1" nameend="c2"><emphasis effect="bold">Chapter Objectives:</emphasis><newline/>
<list id="fs-idm408623760" list-type="bulleted">
<item>Students will be able to analyze the foreign and domestic policies of the Washington and Adams administrations and evaluate the constitutional basis for those policies and the opposition to them.</item>
<item>Students will be able to describe and compare the shaping of a unified American identity across various regions, the reasons for continued regional differences, and the effects of unity or differences in responses to national issues.</item>
</list>
